// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2954 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 4c1c6315-c07b-51fd-9e4c-bfc647c17bf7

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *debian:11* OR ImageFileName = *debian:12* OR ImageFileName = *debian:13* OR ImageFileName = *debian:14*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
